config.title: Write a description of the image below for 1 minute

questions.sampleAnswer: The image shows a young woman sitting at a wooden table in what appears to be a coffee shop or café. She is wearing a striped shirt and has long dark hair. She is holding a white coffee cup and appears to be enjoying her drink. The background is slightly blurred, showing other people and the warm, cozy atmosphere of the café. There are some books or notebooks on the table, suggesting she might be studying or working while having her coffee.

This photograph captures a beautiful mountain landscape during sunset or sunrise. The image shows multiple layers of mountains in the distance, creating a stunning silhouette effect. The sky displays warm colors ranging from orange to pink, creating a peaceful and serene atmosphere. In the foreground, there appears to be some vegetation or trees. The lighting creates a dramatic contrast between the dark mountain shapes and the bright, colorful sky, making this a very scenic and inspiring natural view.

The image shows a professional man in a business suit walking confidently. He appears to be in an urban environment, possibly a business district or office area. The man is well-dressed, wearing a dark suit and carrying what looks like a briefcase or business bag. His posture suggests he is walking with purpose, possibly heading to a meeting or work. The background appears to be blurred, focusing attention on the man in the foreground. The lighting suggests it might be during daytime hours.

This image displays a variety of fresh, healthy foods arranged on a wooden surface. There are numerous colorful vegetables and fruits including tomatoes, avocados, leafy greens, and what appears to be some grains or nuts. The arrangement suggests ingredients for preparing nutritious meals. The presentation is very appealing and emphasizes the importance of eating fresh, natural foods. The wooden background gives the image a rustic, organic feel that complements the healthy food theme.

The photograph shows a modern workspace or office environment. There is a laptop computer open on a clean, white desk. Next to the laptop, there are some office supplies including notebooks, pens, and what appears to be a small plant or succulent for decoration. The workspace looks organized and minimalist, with good lighting that creates a productive atmosphere. This type of setup is typical of modern office work or remote working environments, emphasizing cleanliness and organization.

This image captures a beautiful coastal scene with crystal clear blue water. The photograph shows a pristine beach or coastline with turquoise water that appears very clean and inviting. You can see the sandy bottom through the transparent water, indicating how clear and pure it is. There might be some rocks or coral formations visible beneath the surface. The image conveys a sense of tranquility and natural beauty that you would find in tropical or Mediterranean coastal areas.

The image shows a group of people working together in what appears to be a collaborative office environment. There are several individuals gathered around a table, and they seem to be engaged in a meeting or brainstorming session. Some people are standing while others are seated, and there appear to be documents, laptops, or other work materials on the table. The atmosphere looks professional yet friendly, suggesting good teamwork and communication among colleagues. The setting appears to be a modern office or conference room.

This photograph features a person exercising outdoors, likely going for a run or jog. The individual appears to be wearing athletic clothing suitable for running, such as comfortable workout gear. The setting looks like it could be in a park, along a trail, or in an urban area with green spaces. The image captures the concept of physical fitness and healthy lifestyle choices. The lighting suggests it might be during daytime, providing good conditions for outdoor exercise activities.

The plating style emphasizes both the nutritional value and aesthetic appeal of the food, making it look both healthy and appetizing.

This image captures a family moment with what appears to be parents and children spending time together. The scene conveys the importance of family bonds and quality time spent together. The expressions and body language of the people in the image suggest joy, connection, and the positive aspects of family life.

The photograph shows someone working on a laptop computer in what appears to be a focused work environment. This type of scene is common in today's digital work environment, whether in an office, home office, or co-working space.
